    SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
    FROM `Product` AS `p`
    ORDER BY `p`.`Id`
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS `t`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `t`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `t`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`

FROM (
    SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
    FROM `Product` AS `p`
    ORDER BY `p`.`Id`
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS `t`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `t`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `t`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`

FROM (
    SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`

    ORDER BY `p`.`Id`
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS `t`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `t`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `t`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`

SELECT `t`.`Id`, `t`.`AcquisitionCost`, `t`.`BarCode`, `t`.`CategoryId`, `t`.`DepartmentId`, `t`.`Description`, `t`.`ImageUrl`, `t`.`InventoryCost`, `t`.`InventoryQuantity`, `t`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `t`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Price`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`

    SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
    FROM `Product` AS `p`
    ORDER BY `p`.`Id`
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0
) AS `t`
INNER JOIN `Category` AS `c` ON `t`.`CategoryId` = `c`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `t`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
ORDER BY `t`.`Id`

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
FROM `Category` AS `c`
INNER JOIN `Department` AS `d` ON `c`.`DepartmentId` = `d`.`Id`
LEFT JOIN `Product` AS `p` ON `c`.`Id` = `p`.`CategoryId`
ORDER BY `c`.`Id`, `d`.`Id`

2024-05-15 20:14:57.437 -03:00 [DBG] Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[@__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT `t`.`Id`, `t`.`AcquisitionCost`, `t`.`BarCode`, `t`.`CategoryId`, `t`.`DepartmentId`, `t`.`Description`, `t`.`ImageUrl`, `t`.`InventoryCost`, `t`.`InventoryQuantity`, `t`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `t`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `t`.`Name`, `t`.`Price`, `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`
FROM (
    SELECT `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
    FROM `Product` AS `p`
    ORDER BY `p`.`Id`
    LIMIT @__p_1 OFFSET @__p_0

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`

SELECT `c`.`Id`, `c`.`DepartmentId`, `c`.`Description`, `c`.`Name`, `d`.`Id`, `d`.`Address`, `d`.`CNPJ`, `d`.`Name`, `p`.`Id`, `p`.`AcquisitionCost`, `p`.`BarCode`, `p`.`CategoryId`, `p`.`DepartmentId`, `p`.`Description`, `p`.`ImageUrl`, `p`.`InventoryCost`, `p`.`InventoryQuantity`, `p`.`InventoryUnitMeas`, `p`.`MinimumInventoryQuantity`, `p`.`Name`, `p`.`Price`
